## Workspace Hygiene

- Do not let workspace files grow stale. Update at least one file per session.
- Keep `STATE.md` current — it is the first file loaded.
- Archive old versions of `TENSIONS.md`, `PROPOSALS.md`, and `SELF_MODEL.md` under `workspace/archives/`.
- Never delete a workspace file without archiving it first.
- Prune diary entries older than 90 days into archives.

